        <h2 class="heading-secondary">What is Treasure Dash?</h2>
        <p class="medium-text">Treasure Dash is a simple, free to play browser-based web game. No downloads or sign up are required to play and the rules are simple, which means you can get started playing with your friends or strangers straight away.</p>
    </div>
