        <h2 class="heading-secondary">How was it made?</h2>
        <p class="medium-text">Treasure Dash uses WebSockets with the help of Socket.IO to enable bi-directional communication between clients and the server. The web server is running on NodeJS using the Express web application framework. The source code can be found on <a href="https://github.com/dlh89/treasure-dash">GitHub</a>.</p>
        <p class="medium-text">The project was developed by me, David Hide. I am a full-stack web developer based in the UK. If you are interested in learning more about me or this project, you can find more information on my personal website, <a href="https://davidhide.com">davidhide.com</a>.</p>
